  "detailed_description": "<strong>\"Shooting Donut\"</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2723200/extras/a242361b60492566c2b7bcd909b7e0ce.poster.avif?t=1723250280\" width=500 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2723200/extras/a242361b60492566c2b7bcd909b7e0ce.webm?t=1723250280\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2723200/extras/a242361b60492566c2b7bcd909b7e0ce.mp4?t=1723250280\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Welcome! \"Shooting Donut\" is an immersive puzzle game consisting of a total of 100 thrilling stages. In this game, your goal is to shoot donuts to break candy blocks and progress through the levels.<br><br><br><strong>Game Features:</strong><br>There are 100 diverse stages awaiting you. Each stage provides increasingly complex challenges, requiring you to leverage your brainpower to the fullest.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2723200/extras/de35238ebdfecb94b341190b3d06dd5f.poster.avif?t=1723250280\" width=500 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2723200/extras/de35238ebdfecb94b341190b3d06dd5f.webm?t=1723250280\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2723200/extras/de35238ebdfecb94b341190b3d06dd5f.mp4?t=1723250280\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>To make the game even more enjoyable, four items are at your disposal. These items are designed to assist you in challenging stages. Use the items at the right moment to clear the levels!<br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Finger: Touch and instantly remove the desired candy.<br></li><li>Bomb Donut: Launch an explosive donut to clear surrounding candies in one go.<br></li><li>Bomb: Strategically place bombs to create chain reactions and remove many candies.<br></li><li>Missile: Break through candies as it passes, removing even more candies.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2723200/extras/9bc8a65cefc5d89fb5c0cab3efb1aba1.poster.avif?t=1723250280\" width=500 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2723200/extras/9bc8a65cefc5d89fb5c0cab3efb1aba1.webm?t=1723250280\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2723200/extras/9bc8a65cefc5d89fb5c0cab3efb1aba1.mp4?t=1723250280\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>\"Shooting Donut\" is a shooting puzzle game that can be enjoyed with simple controls. Challenge yourself to achieve high scores within the game!",
